spotify_player is a fast, easy to use, and configurable terminal music player.

Features:
 * Minimalist UI with an intuitive paging and popup system.
 * Highly configurable
 * Feature parity with the official Spotify application.
 * Supports remote control with Spotify Connect.
 * Supports streaming songs directly from the terminal.
 * Supports lyric for most songs.
 * Supports cross-platform media control.
 * Supports image rendering.
 * Supports desktop notification.
 * Supports running the application as a daemon
 * Offers a wide range of CLI commands
